{"tid":2205425,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"唔知點解耐唔時個腦就會出現呢篇嘢","createTime":"2020-09-16T21:40:18.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-17T06:48:04.000Z","uid":359022,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"45122001c6949abfc00ef6f5594d1a95bf2a9d4c","tid":2205425,"uid":359022,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-16T21:40:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n《左 傳‧宣公二年》<br />\n<br />\n晉靈公不君。厚斂以彫牆。從臺上彈人，而觀其辟丸也。宰夫胹熊蹯不孰，殺之，寘諸畚，使婦人載以過朝。趙盾、士季見其手，問其故而患之。將諫，士季曰：「諫而不入，則莫之繼也。會請先，不入，則子繼之。」三進及溜，而後視之。曰：「吾知所過矣，將改之。」稽首而對曰：「人誰無過？過而能改，善莫大焉。詩曰：『靡不有初，鮮克有終。』夫如是，則能補過者鮮矣。君能有終，則社稷之固也，豈惟群臣賴之。又曰：『袞職有闕，惟仲山甫補之。』能補過也。 君能補過，袞不廢矣。」猶不改。宣子驟諫。公患之，使鉏麑賊之。晨往，寢門闢矣。盛服將朝，尚早，坐而假寐。麑退，歎而言曰：「不忘恭敬，民之主也。賊民之主，不忠；弃君之命，不信。有一於此，不如死也。」觸槐而死。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n然後又會想起金仔 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />健在嗎？<br />\n會逼人睇酷刑、猛獸廝殺逆臣<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n中段個故事又d似白雪公主第一次被後母殺嘅事<br />\n個獵人唔捨得殺佢剛好有隻熊撲出黎就殺黎交差<br />\n殺幾次都死唔去，有個版本最後母最後被獵人殺"},{"pid":"e09d19d1c26b3f7b853fae0f6ed9cd59f7c1971b","tid":2205425,"uid":359022,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-16T21:40:54.000Z","msg":"哎呀對唔齊"},{"pid":"d62edf41f10abbb93ec835d15575117ab9757aa5","tid":2205425,"uid":359022,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-16T21:45:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KZfyGwq.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKZfyGwq.png&h=df29a7d8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n突發<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cebcdc6e993fa16fc8609ff30d98712b7851accb","tid":2205425,"uid":362346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-17T06:03:00.000Z","msg":"cls 樓主"},{"pid":"1239d4bc35afccfc9b2abdcdd10e68da591cfb8c","tid":2205425,"uid":359022,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cebcdc6e993fa16fc8609ff30d98712b7851accb","tid":2205425,"uid":362346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-17T06:03:00.000Z","msg":"cls 樓主"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-17T06:48:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}